  "3265070": {
    "name": "筑城记：中世纪",
    "steam_appid": 3265070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/b2b9ce4f5d4416febdbc9a4f5a648136.avif?t=1770715718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras_big/b2b9ce4f5d4416febdbc9a4f5a648136.avif?t=1770715718 width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为人民拥戴的领袖，为他们建设家园、解决生计，进而开疆拓土，建立伟大的王国。无需担忧，领主大人——您的臣民绝不会让您独木难支。各具看家本领的助理们将伴您左右，将自己的命运编织进您亲手谱写的《筑城记》。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/115747da4d90f12baec443dd97493b9c.poster.avif?t=1770715718\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/115747da4d90f12baec443dd97493b9c.webm?t=1770715718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/115747da4d90f12baec443dd97493b9c.mp4?t=1770715718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/e84070bbb5f27d8c5a861bf4a80b964b.avif?t=1770715718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras_big/e84070bbb5f27d8c5a861bf4a80b964b.avif?t=1770715718 width=800 height=129 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多张可选地图：</strong>在两处宜人胜地中选择其一，作为你新王国的起点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自然有机的城市建设：</strong>摒弃 rigid 格栅，利用独特的分区工具塑造自然演进的大型城市。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松的节奏与挑战并存</strong>：在美丽的中世纪世界中享受令人满足的游戏体验，这里的挑战源于你城市及其经济的不断发展。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心系民众的温馨视角：</strong>亲自规划指导助理的技艺成长，让城市建立在民众的需求和愿望之上。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/d2555a3be78b663b47c325b5af2f13c7.poster.avif?t=1770715718\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/d2555a3be78b663b47c325b5af2f13c7.webm?t=1770715718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/d2555a3be78b663b47c325b5af2f13c7.mp4?t=1770715718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/7766ac272f8cae33529a94275394b34b.avif?t=1770715718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras_big/7766ac272f8cae33529a94275394b34b.avif?t=1770715718 width=800 height=123 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>阡陌交通，自然生长</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挣脱网格设计的沉重枷锁，使用独一无二的区域规划工具打造有生命、会呼吸的聚落。村民们经常走过的地方，将自然形成弯弯曲曲的小路，塑造出不断变化的城市与田野风光。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>三教九流，各有念想</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个区域的需求和愿望都取决于居住其中的人们。有些居民喜欢聚集在酒馆，有些则更偏爱教堂带来的宁静。不过，各区域的发展终究要由您的选择指引方向。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>活力经济，深远影响</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日新月异的经济脉搏，由您一手把握。审慎管理资源，迅速决定战略，为城市建设打好基础，点亮中世纪社会发展的指路明灯。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>营造只属于你的荣光之城</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种多样的装饰物供你随心装扮建筑与街道，为城市打上你的独特烙印。繁华盛景，当然要大胆秀出来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/7893aceb281331314bd7234c792cfec4.poster.avif?t=1770715718\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/7893aceb281331314bd7234c792cfec4.webm?t=1770715718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/7893aceb281331314bd7234c792cfec4.mp4?t=1770715718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/ea266bdaf2463ce56577589585b1039a.avif?t=1770715718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras_big/ea266bdaf2463ce56577589585b1039a.avif?t=1770715718 width=800 height=129 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>各具生命轨迹的助理角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与9位同伴携手，为城市经济与故事注入力量与智慧。将他们安排在关键生产节点，通过培训使其具备自主能力并获得额外加成。协助他们完成个人任务，为城市及其居民增添更多深度。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事画卷徐徐展开</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《筑城记》有着柔和的氛围与生动的手绘美术，一砖一石都饱含着妙趣和人情味。自由探索漫步于这片大地的步调，描绘属于自己的精彩故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras/502d96bdbc37300d50e813dc2448b58b.avif?t=1770715718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265070/extras_big/502d96bdbc37300d50e813dc2448b58b.avif?t=1770715718 width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
